snippet.title: The Blackwell Convergence trailer
snippet.description:
Trailer/teaser for the upcoming "Blackwell Convergence" by Wadjet Eye Games.  Rosa and Joey are back!  

Official site: www.wadjeteyegames.com.
Music by: Thomas Regin (www.thomas-regin.com)
Backgrounds by: Luminous Arts and Karen Petrasko
Sprite art by: Shane Stevens (progZmax)
Character portraits by: Ian Schlaepher
Rosa played by: Rebecca Whittaker
Joey played by: Abe Goldfarb
Allen played by: Brian Silliman
